SPEC SHEETS

















About TellurianTellurian Technologies, Inc. has been an innovator in the Frequency Control industry for over 22 years. Founded in 1994, Tellurian has become a worldwide quality supplier of quartz crystals, clock oscillators, TCXO, VCXO, and crystal filters.
In 2001, Tellurian Technologies, Inc. added its VCO product line to complement its quartz frequency devices. SAW Filters and Resonators were added in 2005 to increase the product offering towards full spread spectrum frequency control.
 
Quality in design and manufacture are our Number One priorities. We have built our reputation on supplying frequency based products dock-to-stock, on time or just-in-time from our ISO9001 certified factories.
 
As of 2009, all our products are RoHS compliant. Click Here for our RoHs statement.
 
In keeping with the current requirement for R.E.A.C.H., Click Here for our latest information.
 
All our products use Conflict-Free Material. Click Here for our Conflict-Free statement.

INDUSTRIES

Tellurian Technologies serves many industries including wireless and wireline, aerospace, military and defense to industrial and commercial applications in the medical, data, measurement and energy. Our team of highly experienced engineers are ready to meet specific needs and to design solutions that exceed expectations.


