	(1)


	5.8859 million shares of Magellan common stock were effectively transferred in connection with the Merger. Those shares were valued at $14.03 per share, which was Magellans closing share price on
	February 10, 2017.






	 


	(2)


	Shares issued to former Magellan directors on February 9, 2017.






	 


