	(4)


	Includes a $22.5 million deferred tax asset, with an offsetting $22.5 million valuation allowance.




	 




	(c)


	Adjustments to reflect transaction fees directly related to the Merger that were not reflected in the historical financial statements. Legal and advisory costs are payable to Petrie Partners Securities, LLC
	(Petrie) in approximately 0.4 million shares as a success fee related to the Merger. As these costs are

	non-recurring

	in nature, they have only been reflected within the pro forma balance
	sheet.




	 



















